videos.description: Gonzaga's Josh Perkins tosses it up to Killian Tillie who tosses in the layup in mid-air while getting fouled for an impressive and-1.
videos.headline: Tillie's mid-air tap in leads to Gonzaga's first points

videos.description: San Fran's Nate Renfro finds Matt McCarthy who slams it down with two men on him. On the very next play, Gonzaga's Johnathan Williams finishes on the other end of the floor with another impressive dunk.
videos.headline: Gonzaga and San Francisco trade impressive dunks

videos.description: After a Gonzaga steal, Rui Hachimura takes the fast-break pass and completely throws it down to extend the Zags' lead.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Hachimura shows the rim no mercy

videos.description: Johnathan Williams posts up, turns and sinks a hook shot with a big San Francisco defender in his face.
videos.headline: Williams beats San Fran defender with impressive hook shot

videos.description: San Fransico's Nate Renfro takes a pass from Taavi Jurkatamm and sinks a 3-pointer from deep.
videos.headline: San Fran's Renfro drains 3 from NBA distance

videos.description: Gonzaga's Killian Tillie takes the inbound pass from Josh Perkins then throws it down for 2.
videos.headline: Tillie slams it down off the inbounds pass

videos.description: Dick Vitale and Bob Wischusen discuss Gonzaga's dominating performance over San Francisco, including the impressive play of Killian Tillie who scores 26 points to help the Zags reach their 21st consecutive WCC championship game.
videos.headline: Breaking down Gonzaga's dominant victory
